went aggressive as physicians
making sure that we address

15:00.633 --> 15:02.733 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
pain.

15:02.733 --> 15:05.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Unfortunately, it was found out
later, as we are starting to see
unfold now, we underestimated

15:05.800 --> 15:10.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
the risk related to that
particular high doses
of prescribing those
particular opioids.

15:12.233 --> 15:14.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And now we are suffering
the consequences of that.

15:14.266 --> 15:17.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
