15:24.133 --> 15:26.266 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

15:26.266 --> 15:28.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TRENT HAYWOOD: Well, one of
the things that we know when
it comes to medicine and the

15:28.366 --> 15:32.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
