has a longstanding
historical connection with.

49:04.633 --> 49:09.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SUSAN SCHOELWER, Co-Curator,
Mount Vernon: Nancy Carter
was a young girl, really, who

49:11.700 --> 49:15.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
