49:25.700 --> 49:30.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So when Washington
freed his slaves, then
Nancy Carter was free.

49:30.700 --> 49:35.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She later married Charles
Quander, who was a member
of the Quander family.

49:38.166 --> 49:41.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so there are many
descendants that come
down from that and are
part of the large Quander

49:43.866 --> 49:47.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
family, which, as you
know, is one of the
oldest, if not the oldest,
documented African-American

49:47.866 --> 49:49.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
family in the country.

49:49.833 --> 49:54.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ROHULAMIN QUANDER: The
family history goes back
